{"tid":1353522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喇下次遊行我就唔會嗌「警黑合作」","createTime":"2019-07-23T03:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:47:33.000Z","uid":33875,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"572d1c87b2da4999b501a3f8b6d00554a85342c7","tid":1353522,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"放數開雞竇賣白毒品先係黑社會，爭地盤互斬都係斬返黑幫<br />\n<br />\n但元朗黑夜經歷既係數小時無差別攻擊，由地鐵車站外打到地鐵車廂內，平民百性、男女老幼無一幸免 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n製造公眾恐慌，無人敢出街，無人敢返元屯天，連上西鐵都擔心生命安全受到危害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際關係專家沈旭暉話當晚係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「一場Terrorist Attack（恐怖襲擊）」</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59849879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849879&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUiiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=03c705ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849879&h=28002c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59849879</a></span><br />\n<br />\n黑幫就每個文明大國都有，大家當花生食，但「恐怖襲擊」出現係國際大都會就肯定引起世界關注。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果施襲者，即恐怖分子，懷疑係受到警方包庇，到時你警隊就唔係同香港人交代 </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港大型遊行就一定有外媒隨行，大家到時知道有咩口號可以嗌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"49aad68fcef43959840811a87d6eaf99cd26889a","tid":1353522,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"警黑勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警黑一家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be4158fb0d4f23e29942cb51e582147abaf90db","tid":1353522,"uid":33875,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"49aad68fcef43959840811a87d6eaf99cd26889a","tid":1353522,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"警黑勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警黑一家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"面對外媒，不要說「黑社會」，試著說「恐怖分子」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72486c8976ae1d56b9b34b7b04ae9722989b3265","tid":1353522,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49aad68fcef43959840811a87d6eaf99cd26889a","tid":1353522,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"警黑勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警黑一家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"狼狽為奸"},{"pid":"c8916c84b51a1528905fe13254d78fcf02fa7f26","tid":1353522,"uid":33875,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恐怖襲擊 警察放Break</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7f13fdff9097ad9aa28ac6382c995b02a9db13","tid":1353522,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/07/Untitled-1-1-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2F